\"John\"\n  ],\n  \"sheriff\": null\n}\n\nNow, it is your turn to speak.\nYou are the 6 player to speak this round.\nHere is what the players before you have said:\nAnita: Thank you, Nicholas and Verna, for your reassurance about Manuel's safety. Your statements are very reassuring and show that the Seer is doing their job effectively. I also want to support Margaret and Barbara's observations and encourage everyone to stay vigilant and gather more evidence before making any accusations. While I understand the concerns raised about John and Georgia, I have not noticed any clear signs of suspicious behavior. Let's stay united and work together to protect our village.\nBarbara: Thank you, Anita, for your encouraging words. It's crucial that we continue to stay vigilant and gather as much evidence as possible. While I appreciate the reassurance about Manuel's safety, I have noticed some suspicious behavior that we should keep an eye on. Specifically, I have observed that John and Georgia seem to be spending a lot of time together, and Nicholas and Verna have also been acting in a way that raises my suspicions. However, I want to emphasize that we should not jump to conclusions. We need to gather more information before making any accusations. Let's stay united and work together to protect our village.\nGeorgia: Thank you, Anita and Barbara, for your insightful observations. It's crucial that we continue to stay vigilant and gather as much evidence as possible. While I appreciate the reassurance about Manuel's safety, I have noticed some suspicious behavior that we should keep an eye on. Specifically, I have observed that Nicholas and Verna seem to be spending a lot of time together, and I think we should keep an eye on them as well. However, I want to emphasize that we should not jump to conclusions. We need to gather more information before making any accusations. Let's stay united and work together to protect our village.\nJohn: Thank you, Anita, Barbara, and Georgia